summary: Mainly a file for those looking for a good looking skyrim character and don\'t want to mess around with the character creator.
descriptionHtml:
Kayla is a female Breton, and in my opinion one of the better looking skyrim characters available. Simple for those who don\'t want to waste time with the character creation, and even better, with the beginning of the story which makes this character good for mod practice / usage! 

Earliest save state I could find was at level 3, and I got as far as needed to meet the greybeard\'s about the way of the voice. 

-MODS REQUIRED-

ApaachiiSkyHair - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10168
ApaachiiSkyHair Retexture (Wild Version) - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10357
Better Females by Bella - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2812
No More Blocky Faces - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=30
Really Smooth Female Faces - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=128

-OPTIONAL MODS-

No Dirty Bodies - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=18
Caliente\'s -CBBE- - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666

FOR THE SKIMPY VERSION OF ARMOUR: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=3654

HOW TO USE THE SAVE FILE

I turned off download with manager for obvious reasons as it is made for mod purposes, not save files. 

1) Download
2) Extract Save File
3) Move Save File To Documents > My Games > Skyrim > Saves
4) Launch game, enjoy!
